These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-5-1::.
There 2 different types of food: orange, grapefruit
1. the person eating grapefruit is somewhere to the right of the person eating orange##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2   |
| Food   | orange | grapefruit |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-5-2::.
2 different pets are kept: horse, hamster
1. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hamster##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |  2  |
| Pet   | horse | hamster |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-5-3::.
